the estate of her late billionaire husband, Texas oilman J. Howard Marshall.
U.S. Bankruptcy Judge Samuel Bufford ruled that Marshall's youngest son, E.
Pierce Marshall, had deprived Smith ''of her expectancy of an inheritance.'' Her
attorney, Philip Boesch Jr., said Smith was ''very pleased'' and believes the
ruling ''puts the matter to rest.''
