W. Bush does likewise. Bush had signaled his reluctance to do so just a day
earlier, saying he wanted to get rid of such ads but that Gore couldn't be
counted on to abide by such a deal. ''I don't trust him, to be frank with you,''
the Texas governor said.
</P>
