<HEADLINE> Kafelnikov Wins Gold in Tennis  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   SYDNEY, Australia (AP) -- Yevgeny Kafelnikov of Russia won the
men's singles tennis gold medal Thursday, defeating Tommy Haas of
Germany 7-6, 3-6, 6-2, 4-6, 6-3.
</P>
<P>
   Arnaud Di Pasquale of France won the bronze a day earlier.
</P>
