<HEADLINE> Dow Ends Up 196 Nasdaq Adds 122  </HEADLINE>
By LISA SINGHANIA
<TEXT>
<P>
   NEW YORK (AP) -- Stocks shot higher Thursday, buoyed by rebounds
in technology and blue chip issues as Wall Street regained a
tentative footing amid uncertainty about corporate profits. But an
