Foundation, God's Love We Deliver, Hale House, Citymeals-on-Wheels,
New Yorkers for Children, and The Center for Arts Education.
</P>
<P>
   CowParade featured 500 life-sized cows, decorated in an array of
styles, displayed in all five boroughs from June to September.
